## Naming Convention

### Required Format

```
{review_type}_review_{YYYY-MM-DD}[_context].md
```

**Components:**
- `{review_type}` - Type of review in `snake_case`
- `_review_` - Literal string (required)
- `{YYYY-MM-DD}` - Date of review
- `[_context]` - Optional context (e.g., PR number, feature name)

