## Agent Behavior

### When User Requests Review

1. Determine review type from context
2. Conduct review using appropriate criteria
3. Create report using template above
4. Save to `docs/_reports/reviews/{type}_review_{date}.md`
5. Update `docs/_reports/reviews/README.md` index
6. Report completion to user with link and summary

### Quick Reviews vs Full Reviews

**Quick Review (no formal report):**
- Brief feedback in chat
- No persistent documentation needed
- User just wants quick opinion

**Full Review (formal report):**
- User says "create a review", "document review", "formal review"
- Part of PR process
- Needs to be referenced later
- Compliance/audit requirement

