## How to Use This Rule

**This rule applies when creating any review report.**

**Agents should:**
1. Save all review reports to `docs/_reports/reviews/`
2. Use naming format: `{type}_review_{YYYY-MM-DD}.md`
3. Follow the required template structure
4. Categorize findings clearly
5. Provide clear decision (Approved/Changes/Rejected)
6. Update the review index README.md

**Trigger words:**
- "review", "code review", "pr review"
- "evaluate", "assess", "analyze" (in review context)
- Review command execution

